{"tid":1986840,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"英國路易小王子萌照賀2歲生日　彩虹手印畫象徵希望","createTime":"2020-04-24T05:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T11:28:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd365ac3e7b15688c82bbe0ec36a547b5056d76","tid":1986840,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"英國路易小王子（Prince Louis）今日（23日）2歲生日，英國肯辛頓宮在Twitter發放4張路易小王子的近照慶祝他的生日。照片中，路易小王子雙手沾上彩色顏料，製作彩虹手印畫。英國新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情嚴峻，當地不少孩子都有分享類似的彩虹畫作，象徵希望。<br />\n<br />\n路易小王子身穿藍色格仔襯衫，雙手沾滿彩色顏料，展露可愛笑容。這些照片是今個月於諾福克郡（Norfolk）的家中拍攝，由英國劍橋公爵夫人、路易小王子的媽媽凱特親自拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n路易小王子在2018年4月23日出生，是英國劍橋公爵威廉王子和凱特的第三名孩子，上月英國發起「為醫護鼓掌」（Clap for Carers）行動中，喬治小王子、夏洛特小公主和路易小王子三兄妹亦有拍手致敬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200423/s00005/7867d3fdb1456fcd60c9a6bea12d5036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F7867d3fdb1456fcd60c9a6bea12d5036.jpg&h=a2ad7c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200423/s00005/7867db99eeb8de56d723c3d422ec7287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F7867db99eeb8de56d723c3d422ec7287.jpg&h=80c9c113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200423/s00005/7867ddf1d1fffb747740ec3f0128ccd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F7867ddf1d1fffb747740ec3f0128ccd9.jpg&h=5b9266a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200423/s00005/1587621933150/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%93%E5%B0%8F%E7%8E%8B%E5%AD%90%E8%90%8C%E7%85%A7%E8%B3%802%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5-%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E6%89%8B%E5%8D%B0%E7%95%AB%E8%B1%A1%E5%BE%B5%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F1587621933150%2F%